        <updateDate>2015-11-13T14:35:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Philanthropic Enterprise Act of 2015</strong> </p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to exempt the holdings of a private foundation in any business enterprise that meet specified requirements relating to exclusive ownership, minimum distribution of&nbsp;net operating income for the charitable purpose (all profits to charity distribution requirement), and independent operation (not controlled by a substantial contributor or family members) from the excise taxes on excess business holdings and unrelated business income.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
